.Dt PCHTEMP 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm pchtemp
.Nd Intel PCH Temperature Sensor
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "pchtemp* at pci?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for Intel PCH Temperature Sensor.
.Pp
The
.Nm
driver reports temperatures through the
.Xr envsys 4
API.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr envsys 4 ,
.Xr envstat 8 ,
.Xr powerd 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Nx 12.0 .
